a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball V

p.k: The Boredom / The Vision / The Choices / The Code Gumball and Darwin think it's one of those days when nothing interesting is happening. But as they walk around Elmore it appears exciting things are happening just not to them. / Gumball and Darwin have to stop Alan from becoming Class President of Elmore Junior High. / Nicole remembers the day she first met Richard, and the different choices she could have made. / When the Wattersons' internet cuts out, they have to adapt to a world without it.
